<title>bạftkrlk kl kẖyr</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (yạlly ḥwlt ạlmrạrẗ .. ạlly f ḥyạty ltrnymạt
 ḥty̱ ḍʿfy wjhl qlby .. mạmnʿsẖ ạlạ̹ḥsạnạt)2
 (kl tẖạnyẗ f ʿmry ʿdt .. lw hạtḥky tqwl ktyr
 kl nbḍẗ f qlby gẖnt .. bạftkrlk kl kẖyr)2
 ạlqrạr- (bạftkrlk bạftkrlk)2 .. bạftkrlk kl kẖyr
 2- (ạ̹ḥsạnạtk tạj wṭwq .. ʿly̱ rạsy wʿly̱ qlby
 wjwhr ạltạj ạlly fwq .. dh klh mwt ạlṣlb rby)2
 (dh ạlly kẖlạny ậjy sạjd .. wạ̉ḥny rạsy wạqwl ṣgẖyr
 bạlṣlyb ạ̉nạ ṣrt wạjd .. fy ạlmsyḥ nʿm ạlmṣyr)2
 3- (lwlạ mskẗ ạ̹ydk ạ̹nt .. knt ạ̉ḍyʿ wyạ ạlly ḍạʿ
 ạ̉nạ msẖ ạ̉fḍl mn ạlly .. kẖạn wạ̉nkr wạlly bạʿ)2
 (qlby mdywn lk yạ gẖạly .. ʿmry klh hạʿysẖ ạ̉syr
 nʿmtk rạ̉ft bḥạly .. wrạḥ tkml yạ qdyr)2</lyrics>
</song>